{"tid":1557483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【極危險】白衫佬已經滲透日常生活，隨時斬人！！","createTime":"2019-09-10T06:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T07:59:19.000Z","uid":6980,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"da8724b9b363fa8554ab60e2e99669d82c3a0599","tid":1557483,"uid":6980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:36:37.000Z","msg":"我朋友(不是我)嘅親身經歷<br />\n早幾日佢同個fd喺發夢地點附近call uber返屋企 <br />\n但佢哋唔係發完夢，只係咁啱喺附近<br />\n個司機不停chok佢地係咪去完示威<br />\n我個fd就chok返佢轉頭，原來個司機住元朗南邊圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個司機又話自己平時做冷氣維修，車尾箱有架餐都好合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又問我fd去將軍澳係咪示威(嗰晚圍緊黨鐵)<br />\n嚇到我fd求其喺tko黨鐵附近落車狗衝走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">極度懷疑白衫佬已經滲透全城<br />\n隨時抆刀斬人！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n就算唔係去發夢<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">大家平時出街call uber都要加倍小心</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">一見到個司機唔對路就馬上落車<br />\n唔好同陌生人傾任何關於示威嘅嘢<br />\n有外人同車嘅時候同朋友傾計都要小心啲<br />\n提防白衫佬鎖定你係目標</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088494be133288182d19a56ca18e303ee919c361","tid":1557483,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:42:38.000Z","msg":"記車牌號碼 告佢渣白牌車"},{"pid":"59784cf774263002b4615365f63dcb29c810d660","tid":1557483,"uid":6980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:43:09.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e38b7b2eb473a9fe81812c33896177a0ca8087","tid":1557483,"uid":16109,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:44:17.000Z","msg":"你一係出Uber 資料，唔係當fa